 Allowed</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry><p>Rx, Tx</p></entry><entry><p>2</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="SECTION_1AE7DE41-B1F4-427A-BAC1-8BE10BFFE4BE"><title>Mainstream, Premium Mid Loss (PML), Rx,Tx</title><table id="TABLE_1AE7DE41-B1F4-427A-BAC1-8BE10BFFE4BE_1"><title>CNVio3 M.2 Topology Mainstream, Premium Mid Loss (PML), Rx,Tx Routing Guidelines</title><tgroup cols="4"><thead><row><entry>Segment</entry><entry>Tline Type</entry><entry>Max Length Segment (mm)</entry><entry>Max Length Segment Note</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry><p>BO</p></entry><entry><p>MS, SL</p></entry><entry><p>13</p></entry><entry><p /></entry></row><row><entry><p>M1</p></entry><entry><p>SL</p></entry><entry><p /></entry><entry><p>BO + M1 + M2 &lt;= 178</p></entry></row><row><entry><p>M2</p></entry><entry><p>MS</p></entry><entry><p>17</p></entry><entry><p /></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><p>Max Length Total (mm): 178</p></section></body></topic>